{"tid":848783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新型騙案 冒充積金局員工來電","createTime":"2018-10-05T07:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T08:27:46.000Z","uid":209890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49ddc0d608aa89dc086f0af77d000e4294cb4c9f","tid":848783,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:54:23.000Z","msg":"電話係2119 5742<br />\n話說前日<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">扮緊工</span></strong><br />\n突然依個電話號碼就打黎<br />\n問我他唔係機主<br />\n我話係啦。但注意佢係無講過我姓乜名乜<br />\n就話佢係強積金打黎<br />\n話要約我出黎面對面重整計劃<br />\n問我九龍新界香港邊區方便<br />\n我一開始話唔洗啦<br />\n咁佢就話無話唔洗既<br />\n香港人每一個人都要既<br />\n我心諗每個人你都約出黎見咁你十年都見唔晒啦<br />\n我就知佢絕對唔正路<br />\n所以我答佢咁今晚12點和合石等然後收佢線喇<br />\n上網查一查果然。。。"},{"pid":"a895e1376275962af1b5768bb49f1c902c4ab77d","tid":848783,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:19:22.000Z","msg":"我都有過咁嘅電話 話下星期一要調整翻強積金計劃 邊日得閒約出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3685b32619c19baea2833ca5b1957ec40d0060f","tid":848783,"uid":1219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:21:08.000Z","msg":"約佢再放飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0908ec6eaf79276ab0fd1167002d339de0d0d36","tid":848783,"uid":9315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3685b32619c19baea2833ca5b1957ec40d0060f","tid":848783,"uid":1219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:21:08.000Z","msg":"約佢再放飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"約去隔涉既地方或者有minimum charge/淨飲雙計既餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783f85e8c9af308a3285c1c1c9217ae5cac888a6","tid":848783,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\